	"keywords": "7Days7Websites, Coding Challenge",
	"description": "I believe that one of the best ways to improve your coding skills is to CODE\nMORE!\n\nFor that I have the perfect challenge for you! ?\n\nIt&#x27;s called: #7Days7Websites\n\nThe main rule is simple: build one website, every day, for a week.\n\nHere is a short video I made to explain everything in more detail:\n\nYou can find the official website here [https://7days7websites.glitch.me/].\n\nRules\n * Create a website every day for a week.\n * You can use any programming language and/or any framework you want.\n * T",
