	"description": "One month ago I embarked on a challenge that many people told me was insane. I\nset out to conquer the entire freeCodeCamp curriculum. All while live streaming\neverything on my YouTube channel\n[https://youtube.com/florinpop?sub_confirmation&#x3D;1].\n\n29 days, 56 Live Streams\n[https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list&#x3D;PLgBH1CvjOA62oNEVgz-dECiCZCE_Q3ZFH] and \n72 hours of live streams later...\n\n&gt; ??? We did it! ???\n\nAfter:\n- 29 days\n- 56 Live Streams \n- 72 hours of content\n- 6 sections\n- 30 projects\n\nWe comp",
