	"description": "Today is Valentines Day! ?\n\nHow nice would it be if you sent a Romantic Message every hour to your loved\none? But even better...\n\nHow awesome would it be to do it automatically using a Node.js script? We are\nafter all... programmers, right? ?\n\nIn this short tutorial I&#x27;m going to show you how to do it.\n\nP.S. For the lazy ones out there, here is a Video Tutorial:\n\nCreate a CRON job\nFirst, we need to create a CRON job which will run a function every hour.\n\nFor that, let&#x27;s install the node-cron pack",
